topic.title: Family History Section (V3) - conformance rules

section.p: This section contains data defining the patient's genetic relatives in terms of possible or relevant health risk factors that have a potential impact on the patient's healthcare risk profile.

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:1198-7932, CONF:1198-10388, CONF:1198-32607 ) such that it
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.2.15"
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @extension="2015-08-01"
SHALL conform to Family History Section[Section: templateId 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.2.15] template (templateId: 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.2.15)

If section/@nullFlavor is not present, MAY contain [0..*] entry such that it (CONF:1198-32430, CONF:1198-32431)
Conforms to Family History Organizer2[Organizer: templateId 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.45] (templateId: 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.45:2015-08-01)
SHALL conform to Family History Section[Section: templateId 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.2.15] template (templateId: 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.2.15)

SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code (CONF:15469, R2.1=CONF:1198-15469)/@code="10157-6" Family History (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.6.1 LOINC) (CONF:15470, R2.1=CONF:1198-15470, R2.1=CONF:1198-32481)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] title (CONF:7934, R2.1=CONF:1198-7934)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] text (CONF:7935, R2.1=CONF:1198-7935)

If section/@nullFlavor is not present, MAY contain [0..*] entry such that it (CONF:1198-32430, CONF:1198-32431)
Conforms to Family History Organizer2[Organizer: templateId 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.45] (templateId: 2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.45:2015-08-01)
